            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Убедитесь, что мы не обрабатываем завершенные задачи.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"tasks = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;pending&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;completed&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;pending&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;pending&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"index = \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" index &lt; len(tasks):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" tasks[index] == \" /><text value=\"&quot;completed&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Skipping task \" /><text value=\"{index + \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    index += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"continue\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Processing task \" /><text value=\"{index + \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  index += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"185\" endIndex=\"193\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"break\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"else\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Processing task 1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Skipping task 2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Processing task 3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Processing task 4\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>continue</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
