            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Обязательно исправь ошибки, прежде чем продолжать с списком дел.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"tasks = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;email boss&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;fix bug&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;attend meeting&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" task \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" tasks:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" task == \" /><text value=\"&quot;fix bug&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Urgent task found: fix bug&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"break\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Working on: \" /><text value=\"{task}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"77\" endIndex=\"81\" /><option startIndex=\"82\" endIndex=\"84\" /><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"94\" /><option startIndex=\"140\" endIndex=\"145\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"else\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"continue\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Working on: email boss\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Urgent task found: fix bug\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>task</code>, затем <code>==</code>, а затем <code>\"fix bug\"</code>, <code>break</code>.</p></body></html>"
